<emphasis box="[842,921,1962,1985]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">securis</emphasis>
, meaning axe, and 
<emphasis box="[1164,1232,1961,1985]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">cauda</emphasis>
, meaning tail. It describes the sharp, blade-like keel of the animalâ€™s tail.
</paragraph>
